The website should have a video tutorial feature that helps users learn 
how to make the dish in the recipe. When the user clicks on a specific 
recipe, the website should display a relevant video tutorial that shows 
how to make the dish step by step. The user should be able to watch the 
video within the recipe page without having to navigate to a different 
page or website. The video displayed should be the most relevant 
tutorial on YouTube when searching for the specific recipe. This feature 
will help users learn how to make the dish in the recipe and increase 
their cooking skills.
